svg.title: gofingo KZ
svg.desc: Gofingo.kz is a part of a private holding company, which successfully operates in the Czech Republic, Denmark, Lithuania and Ukraine since 2015. Established in 2018, Gofingo.kz, has managed to build a well-performing portfolio relatively quickly. Because of the international experience of their specialists, they provide simple, fast and transparent services. Listed loans on the platform will range from 16 Eur up to 350 Eur. Additionally, some things haven't changed with a new loan originator: all loans are secured with 100% buyback guarantee.
